<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qgamepadmanager.xml">QGamepadManager</db:link> provides a high-level interface for querying the attached gamepads and events related to all of the connected devices.</db:para>
</db:section>
